== Reporting issues with third-party code ==

Bugs or security issues in the libraries listed above should be reported to
their upstream projects. Bugs in Sleezer's integration of them — or in code
that originated in `Lidarr.Plugin.Deezer` or `Tubifarry` and has been merged
here — belong on the Sleezer issue tracker:
    https://github.com/chodeus/sleezer/issues
